            <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>小众豆瓣已成刚需，电影、图书看完都会标记下，写日志时常会提到，老想着在文章内「优雅」地展示，官方 API 已废，<del>幸好还有给力的 <a href="https://mufeng.me/">@mufeng</a> 兄，以下功能就使用其提供的轮子。</del></p>
<p>换用轮子：<a href="https://github.com/cxfksword/douban-api-rs">https://github.com/cxfksword/douban-api-rs</a></p>
<h3 id="效果如下">效果如下</h3>
<p><a href="https://movie.douban.com/subject/34953719/">https://movie.douban.com/subject/34953719/</a></p>
<p><a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/35254632/">https://book.douban.com/subject/35254632/</a></p>
<h3 id="使用方式">使用方式</h3>
<p>如果是md的话之间输入以下格式，其他输入a标签链接，注意链接以 <code>/</code> 斜杠结尾。</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-html" data-lang="html"><span style="display:flex;"><span>&lt;<span style="color:#f92672">https:</span><span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">//</span><span style="color:#a6e22e">movie</span><span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">.</span><span style="color:#a6e22e">douban</span><span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">.</span><span style="color:#a6e22e">com</span><span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">/</span><span style="color:#a6e22e">subject</span><span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">/</span><span style="color:#a6e22e">34953719</span>/&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>&lt;<span style="color:#f92672">https:</span><span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">//</span><span style="color:#a6e22e">book</span><span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">.</span><span style="color:#a6e22e">douban</span><span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">.</span><span style="color:#a6e22e">com</span><span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">/</span><span style="color:#a6e22e">subject</span><span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">/</span><span style="color:#a6e22e">35254632</span>/&gt;
</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id="相关代码">相关代码</h3>
<p>head 头部添加 meta ：</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-html" data-lang="html"><span style="display:flex;"><span>&lt;<span style="color:#f92672">meta</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">name</span><span style="color:#f92672">=</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;referrer&#34;</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">content</span><span style="color:#f92672">=</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;no-referrer&#34;</span>&gt;
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>基于 jQuery 的功能代码，内置自建 API 不保证稳定（瞬间被502，哎……）：</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e">//豆瓣图书电影条目
