<p>详细使用参考： <a href="https://www.zhangxinxu.com/wordpress/2014/08/image-dominant-color-get-rgbaster-js/">https://www.zhangxinxu.com/wordpress/2014/08/image-dominant-color-get-rgbaster-js/</a></p>
